{"type": "article", "id": 11785, "title": "随身鸡尾酒调配套组合", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-08T11:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061356070GSNZH1Xs3liTef8.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自纽约的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://wandpdesign.com/\" target=\"_blank\">W&amp;P Design </a>和<a href=\"http://punchdrink.com/\" target=\"_blank\">线上杂志 Punch </a>联手推出了一套名为 “Carry On Cocktail” 的随身鸡尾酒调配套组合。一个锡制的盒子里面配有配料和小型的工具，有配方卡片，勺子，量杯，杯垫等等，而口味分为老式杜松子酒和金汤力，让你在旅途中也能够享受调酒的乐趣。产品售价 24 美元，<a href=\"http://carryoncocktailkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261358215IpJsEfrjcRbXWSz.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135821FR4tl1AUwfS53gIq.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"439\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.40648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135822OB8SPpVYuc4nHU9L.jpg\" width=\"780\" height=\"521\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135822qTltLnW73kHAuC1M.jpg\" width=\"780\" height=\"519\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135823yzEBgevWC8GYrq5u.jpg\" width=\"780\" height=\"519\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}